            <lg xml:id="TK1196">
<l>orutalaiyā ṉiṉṉātu kāmaṅkāp pōla </l>
<l> virutalai yāṉum miṉitu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Lust, like the weight of the KAVADI, pains if it lies in one end only but pleases if it is in both.</l>
